weather app is the interesting app to make to learn about fetch api and promises , synchronous and asynchronous function.
async and await function

to install tailwind css 
first install dev dependencies package of tailwind
npm install -D tailwind 
now create a configuration file in using the command "npx tailwind init" in the terminal.
from the tailwind css documentation there we can find the file called tailwind.config.js now every content from that file is copied and pasted to the tailwind.config.js in your project folder.
now add 3 utilities in index.css;
now npm start your site 
because tailwind will be only effective after restarting the server.
In useEffect()
we have to write 
useEffect(()=>{
    //this area is for call back function 
},[//this part is fpr dependencies])